data.text:
Mr. Timothy Alan Keen, age 52, of Westmoreland, TN

passed away Thursday, December 11, 2014.

Funeral services for Mr. Keen will be held Sunday, December 14, 2014 at 2:00 PM from Woodard Funeral Home with Bro. Lance Carter officiating.

Visitation will be: Friday, December 12, 2014 from 3:00 PM to 9:00 PM at Woodard Funeral Home and Saturday, December 13, 2014 from 10:00 AM to 9:00 PM at Woodard Funeral Home and Sunday, December 14, 2014 from 10:00 AM to 2:00 PM at Woodard Funeral Home.

Mr. Keen was a member of Garretts Creek General Baptist Church and Westmoreland Historical Society.

He was preceded in death by his:

Step-Father - Lowell Gilliam,

Nephew - Adam Keene,

Grand Parents - Owen and Eunice Keen, and Lowell and Frances Willoughby,

Mr. Keen is survived by his:

Wife - Freda Keen, Westmoreland, TN

Daughter - Sara Ann Keen, Westmoreland, TN

Mother - Margie Gilliam, Westmoreland, TN

Father - James Henry Keene(Barbara), Portland, TN

Brother - Michael Keene, Westmoreland, TN

Brother - Jeffery Keene(Lisa), Westmoreland, TN

Step-Brother - Jeff Hunter, Portland, TN

Nephew - Chris Keene (Channon), Westmoreland, TN

Niece - Stephanie Brewington

Niece - Kim Green(Bear), Lafayette, TN

NOTE: In lieu of flower the family request you make donations to the Vanderbilt Bladder Cancer Research.
